[...]
suggest you start with the light switch itself.   These are usually 
multicontact switches.  Several times i have chased mysterious light 
problems back to the main light switch and burned out contacts inside. 
(rabbit lost all dash lights, jetta lost tail lights, bug lost 
everything)
jimt
